text: Maga nuhanantara amhi dusarya paigambaranna tyancya janasamuhakade pathavile tevha te tyancyajavala spasta pramana ghe'una ale, parantu jya gostila tyanni pahilya khepesa khote tharavile, nantara ticyavara imana rakhale asate ase jhale nahi. Asa prakare amhi maryada para karanaryancya hrdayanva mohara lavato
